1.
Terminal report. Rich CLI output showing verdicts, confidence intervals, -values, effect sizes, and coverage metrics for each scenario.
-
2.
HTML report. Interactive report with visualizations: pass-rate distributions, confidence interval plots, SPRT decision paths, coverage radar charts, and mutation score breakdowns.
